      <p></p>
<p>Losing a friend is like losing a piece of yourself.  The pain can be immense, and words may feel inadequate.  However, a simple message of support can mean the world to someone navigating this difficult time. Let your friend know you are present to listen and offer support without judgment.</p>
<li>I am so sorry to hear about the loss of your friend.</li>
<li>My heart aches for you.</li>
<li>Sending you love and strength during this painful time.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and sending you all my love.</li>
<li>I am here for you if you need anything at all.</li>
